W06_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_DETAIL.text: On the other side of the door was a world that is very much alive. Will you find a cat here?

W06_EVAR_AMYA_RETURN_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W06_EVAR_AMYA_RETURN_000_DETAIL.text: You've found your cat. Time to head back to Miyako City.

W06_EVAR_AMYA_NEKO_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W06_EVAR_AMYA_NEKO_000_DETAIL.text: A cat must be around here somewhere.
